OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,FOn 2 May, local elections will be
OL,7,Ftaking place across the country.
OL,9,FIn our region, that will include votes
OL,10,Ffor three directly-elected metro
OL,11,Fmayors.
OL,13,FPlans for metro mayors were introduced
OL,14,Fby the government as part of
OL,15,Fdevolution agreements to give people
OL,16,Fpeople more power over local decision-
OL,17,Fmaking.
OL,19,FMetro mayors are elected by the public
OL,20,Fand serve a term of four years.
