OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,FThey hold substantial powers and
OL,7,Ffunding over areas including job
OL,8,Fcreation and skills, housing and
OL,9,Ftransport - though these powers can
OL,10,Fvary depending on the terms of the
OL,11,Fdevolution deal which was signed to
OL,12,Fcreate them.
OL,14,FThey will also chair the combined
OL,15,Fauthority for that area, which is made
OL,16,Fup of the councils within it. They are
OL,17,Falso viewed as a regional figurehead,
OL,18,Frepresenting their area on the
OL,19,Fnational stage.
