OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,FThere are three metro mayoral
OL,7,Felections taking place within our
OL,8,Fregion on 2 May.
OL,10,FThe position of North East Mayor is
OL,11,Fnew and will replace the existing
OL,12,FNorth of Tyne Mayor.
OL,14,FAs well as the existing area covered
OL,15,Fby that role, the North East Mayoral
OL,16,FCombined Authority will now include
OL,17,FCounty Durham, Gateshead, Sunderland
OL,18,Fand South Tyneside too.
