OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,F, the new North East Mayor will have
OL,7,Fdevolved powers on employment and
OL,8,Fskills, planning and regeneration and
OL,9,Feconomic development in the region.
OL,11,FCrucially, unlike its North of Tyne
OL,12,Fpredecessor, the new North East mayor
OL,13,Fwill also have powers over transport.
OL,15,FThese will include responsibility for
OL,16,Fthe Tyne and Wear Metro, longer-term
OL,17,Fspending on transport and the power to
OL,18,Fintroduce bus franchising.
