OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,FThe role of Tees Valley Mayor has
OL,7,Fexisted since 2017. This year will
OL,8,Fmark the third opportunity for voters
OL,9,Fon Teesside to elect a metro mayor.
OL,11,FThe Tees Valley Combined Authority
OL,12,Fcovers Darlington, Stockton,
OL,13,FHartlepool, Middlesbrough and Redcar &
OL,14,FCleveland. The mayor here will have
OL,15,Fpower over transport, skills and
OL,16,Finvestment.
OL,18,FThis will be the first time that
OL,19,Fvoters will be able to choose a York &
OL,20,FNorth Yorkshire Mayor, after a
OL,21,Fdevolution deal was signed off in 2022.
