OL,3,CWhat responsibilities will the metro
OL,4,Cmayors have in the North East?
OL,6,FAs the name suggests, it will bring
OL,7,Ftogether the council areas of North
OL,8,FYorkshire and City of York.
OL,10,FLike the others, this mayor will have
OL,11,Fresponsibility for issues such as
OL,12,Fhousing, skills and transport.
OL,13,FHowever, they will have the added
OL,14,Fresponsibility of policing and
OL,15,Ftackling crime.
OL,17,FPolls will be open between 7am and
OL,18,F10pm on Thursday 2 May, when a number
OL,19,Fof other elections are also taking
OL,20,Fplace across the region .
